description:
This is a special &quot;embedded subs&quot; version of the Czech black-and-white sci-fi classic, IKARIE XB1 (1963) for Google Chromecast. 

Audio track is in the Czech language. English subtitles are &quot;hard-embedded&quot; on screen.

There is also an English-audio-dubbed VHS RIP available with the name &quot;Voyage to the End of the Universe&quot;. However, the video quality of that version is horrible.

Google Chromecast supports just a limited number of video and audio codecs and container file types. Chromecast still does not handle subtitles, so the English subtitles have been overlayed directly on the video image with this download.

Video: H264 ( 720 x 404 ) --- Audio: AAC (m4a) stereo 48000

This small but quality movie file with embedded subtitles was created using VLC and Avanti.
